# How to run?

## STEPS:

Clone the repository

```bash
https://github.com/Artom121/CNN-end2end
```

### STEP 01 - create a conda enviroment

```bash
create conda -n kidney python=3.8 -y
```

```bash
conda activate kidney
```

### STEP 02 - install the requirements

```bash
pip install -r requirements.yaml
```

